high_descs: Turn left walk toward dishwasher, Turn left and walk toward counter next to oven
pick up lettuce and bring it to front of counter
take lettuce over the counter next to the toaster
put lettuce on counter
pick up knife on the left
cut lettuce into slices
set the knife down between slices on counter top
pick up a lettuce slice off of the counter
take lettuce slice over to stove
set lettuce into the pot
remove the pot from off the stove
walk over to the counter to the right of the sink
set the pot on the counter
anns.task_desc: How to slice and cook a lettuce slice

high_descs: Go to the counter just past the stove on the right.
Pick up the lettuce leaf on top of the cell phone.
Move over to the counter next to the toaster.
Lay the lettuce leaf down on the counter.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter.
Slice the lettuce on the counter into pieces.
Set the butter knife down on top of the lettuce.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Go to the stove.
Put the lettuce in the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot with the lettuce in it.
Walk over to the counter next to the sink.
Set the pot down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with lettuce in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and cross the room to the sink, then turn left and walk to the counter in front of you
Pick up the lettuce that is on the counter
Step to the left
Place the lettuce on the counter.
Pick up the knife that is on the left side of the lettuce, the butter knife.
Slice the lettuce
Place the knife on the counter in between the lettuce slices
Pick up a slice of lettuce
Turn around then walk to the stove on your left
Place the lettuce in the pot on the stove
Pick up the pot that contains the lettuce
Turn to your right and walk to the microwave then turn left and face the counter to the right of the sink
Place the pot containing the lettuce on the counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a pot containing lettuce on a counter

high_descs: Turn around and head to the counter to the left of the oven
Grab the lettuce that is on the counter
Move slightly to the left
Put the lettuce on the counter
Grab the small knife off of the counter
Cut the lettuce into slices
Put the knife down on the counter
Grab a slice of lettuce
Turn right and stop at the oven
Put the lettuce in the pot on the stove
Grab the pot with the lettuce in it
Turn right and stop at the counter to the right of the sink
Put the pot on the counter
anns.task_desc: Moving a pot with a slice of lettuce in it to the counter
